# Build inputs for the installer go here:
#   agent.exe         (from `cd agent && make build-windows`)
#   watchdog.ps1      (copy from `installer/watchdog.ps1`)
#   python.zip        (Python embeddable for Windows, ~35MB)
#   ai-client.py      (your AI thin-client entry point)
#
# These files are bundled into setup.exe at compile time via go:embed.
# This .gitkeep file holds the directory in git; do not commit large
# binaries here — instead have CI fetch them from a release artifact store.
